{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/experience/1/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"보통사람","author":"pej4303"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"183a6227-8fa9-55ef-b54f-ee09314b7ea8","excerpt":"1. 💡 현상 iframe을 이용해 화면을 구성하고 있는 상황에서 단축키를 눌러 특정 버튼을 동작시키려고 했으나 화면을 한 번 클릭한 뒤에만 단축키가 동작하는 문제가 발생했다. 2. 🔍 원인 키보드 이벤트 자체는 잡히지만 버튼 요소는 iframe…","html":"<h2 id=\"1--현상\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1--%ED%98%84%EC%83%81\" aria-label=\"1  현상 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 💡 현상</h2>\n<p>iframe을 이용해 화면을 구성하고 있는 상황에서 단축키를 눌러 특정 버튼을 동작시키려고 했으나<br>\n<strong>화면을 한 번 클릭한 뒤에만 단축키가 동작하는</strong> 문제가 발생했다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2--원인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2--%EC%9B%90%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"2  원인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 🔍 원인</h2>\n<p>키보드 이벤트 자체는 잡히지만 <strong>버튼 요소는 iframe 내부에 있기 때문에 이벤트를 받아도 버튼을 탐지하지 못하는</strong> 상황이었다.<br>\n즉, 현재 문서(document) 기준으로 버튼을 찾으려고 했기 때문에 iframe 내부 버튼에는 접근할 수 없었다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3--해결-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3--%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"3  해결 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. ✅ 해결 방법</h2>\n<p>현재 문서가 iframe이면 <strong>iframe 내부에서 버튼을 찾고</strong><br>\n그 외에는 현재 문서에서 버튼을 찾도록 분기 처리하였다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"-개선된-코드\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EA%B0%9C%EC%84%A0%EB%90%9C-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C\" aria-label=\" 개선된 코드 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🔧 개선된 코드</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 기존 소스</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ctrlKey <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>key <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Enter'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> $btn <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.search:visible'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>$btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    $btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">first</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">trigger</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 변경된 소스</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ctrlKey <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>key <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Enter'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> iframe <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'iframe'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> $searchScope <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> iframe <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>iframe<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>contentWindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> $btn <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> $searchScope<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.search:visible'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>$btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    $btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">first</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">trigger</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>📚 참조\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLIFrameElement/contentWindow\">iframe.contentWindow 설명 (MDN)</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1--%ED%98%84%EC%83%81\">1. 💡 현상</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2--%EC%9B%90%EC%9D%B8\">2. 🔍 원인</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#3--%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">3. ✅ 해결 방법</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#-%EA%B0%9C%EC%84%A0%EB%90%9C-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C\">🔧 개선된 코드</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[JS] iframe 안에서 단축키 이벤트가 동작하지 않는 문제","description":"[JS] iframe 안에서 단축키 이벤트가 동작하지 않는 문제","date":"July 27, 2025","tags":["해결","jQuery","iframe"],"series":"해결","previewImage":"writing-help.png","isPrivate":true}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/archive/algorithm/31/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[백준] 숨바꼭질 Java","isPrivate":false}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"183a6227-8fa9-55ef-b54f-ee09314b7ea8","previousPostId":"acbee884-a300-5017-a341-d020dfa912b2","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}